 drivers/gpu/drm/radeon/radeon.h        |  4 ++
 drivers/gpu/drm/radeon/radeon_ttm.c    | 77 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 3 files changed, 81 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

